WEBVTT

00:03:27.506 --> 00:03:30.336
I believe that human beings have the power

00:03:30.360 --> 00:03:34.387
to turn situations of poverty
into those of wealth and prosperity.

00:03:34.789 --> 00:03:37.701
We have the capacity
to alleviate suffering,

00:03:37.725 --> 00:03:40.948
extend life, prevent diseases,

00:03:40.972 --> 00:03:44.331
cure debilitating ailments,
reduce infant mortality

00:03:44.355 --> 00:03:46.022
and preserve our planet.

00:03:46.442 --> 00:03:51.124
